SEO plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO is an established plugin with thousands of 5-star reviews on WordPress.org. And over 3 million people have downloaded it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-140989\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-768x364.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-190x90.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage.png 1260w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>While AIOSEO offers several paid versions of the plugin, you can use the free version indefinitely. It has no cut-off date.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-benefits-of-aioseo-lite\">Benefits of AIOSEO Lite</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO makes it easy to set up WordPress SEO the right way. Here are some of the benefits of AIOSEO Lite:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Sitemap</strong>: Get an XML sitemap automatically generated for you.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>On-Page SEO made easy</strong>: The plugin will automatically analyze your pages and tell you how to improve your SEO.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Boost engagement </strong>by acting on our readability recommendations.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Optimize</strong> your posts, pages, and custom post types.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Social media optimization</strong>: Control precisely how your pages look when shared on social platforms.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Sell </strong>more products with SEO by using our WooCommerce integration.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Apply schema markup</strong>: Get rich snippets for a sitelinks searchbox, breadcrumb schema, and person and organization pages.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Integrate with <strong>Microsoft Clarity</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-general-settings-1024x507.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo lite sidebar\" class=\"wp-image-225334\" style=\"width:699px;height:346px\" width=\"699\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-general-settings-1024x507.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-general-settings-300x149.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-general-settings-768x381.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-general-settings-1536x761.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-general-settings-2048x1015.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-general-settings-600x297.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-general-settings-121x60.jpg 121w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/aioseo-general-settings-182x90.jpg 182w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Above: AIOSEO appears as a sidebar in your WordPress editor.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to this, if you upgrade to the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">Pro version</a>, you’ll get access to the following.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Rich snippets: </strong>Easily turn your pages into rich snippets. Get access to 18 types of schema. These include schema for recipes, courses, books, events, job listings, datasets, etc.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>AI-Powered Link Assistant</strong>: Boost SEO by adding internal links the smart way. Fix orphan pages and track affiliate links.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Local SEO</strong>: Use these tools to get your small business noticed in local search results. Includes Google Maps integration.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>RSS Sitemap</strong>: All in One SEO (AIOSEO) automatically generates and updates this sitemap for you. Keep Google updated on new content with this sitemap.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Video Sitemap</strong>: Make it easier for Google to find and rank your video pages.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Images SEO module</strong>: Automatically set image alt text and title attributes for images.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Redirection Manager</strong>: Automate redirects and prevent 404s the easy way.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Google News Sitemap</strong>: This specialized sitemap is for news content. Integrates with Google News.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>ChatGPT integration</strong>: Experiment with auto-generating meta descriptions and titles.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Priority customer support</strong>: Our world-class support team is delighted to assist.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/#pricing-table\">And more</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"564\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-1024x564.jpg\" alt=\"rich snippet example\" class=\"wp-image-203449\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-1024x564.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-300x165.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-768x423.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-1536x846.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-2048x1127.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-600x330.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-109x60.jpg 109w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-163x90.jpg 163w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Above: The Pro version of AIOSEO makes it easy to turn product pages into rich snippets like these.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Pro version covers up to 10 sites and includes unlimited users, SEO audits, and keyword analysis.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons alignwide is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-8 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-text-align-center wp-element-button\" href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">Get AIOSEO Pro Now</a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-how-do-i-install-the-all-in-one-seo-aioseo-free-version-aioseo-lite\">How Do I Install the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) Free Version (AIOSEO Lite)?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Follow these simple steps to get AIOSEO for free.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-1-download-aioseo-lite-from-wordpress-org\">Step 1: Download AIOSEO Lite from WordPress.org</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Go to the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">WordPress.org page</a>. Click the blue Download button at the right.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/download-aioseo-lite-1024x540.jpg\" alt=\"download free aioseo\" class=\"wp-image-229868\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/download-aioseo-lite-1024x540.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/download-aioseo-lite-300x158.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/download-aioseo-lite-768x405.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/download-aioseo-lite-1536x809.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/download-aioseo-lite-2048x1079.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/download-aioseo-lite-600x316.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/download-aioseo-lite-114x60.jpg 114w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/download-aioseo-lite-171x90.jpg 171w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO Lite will download to your computer as a zip file.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-2-install-the-all-in-one-seo-aioseo-lite-plugin\">Step 2: Install the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) Lite Plugin</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, log into your WordPress website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the left-hand navigation, click on <strong>Plugins</strong> and select <strong>Add New</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"339\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-add-new-plugin-1024x339.png\" alt=\"wordpress add new plugin\" class=\"wp-image-210593\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-add-new-plugin-1024x339.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-add-new-plugin-300x99.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-add-new-plugin-768x255.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-add-new-plugin-1536x509.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-add-new-plugin-2048x679.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-add-new-plugin-600x199.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-add-new-plugin-181x60.png 181w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-add-new-plugin-272x90.png 272w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, at the top of your page, click <strong>Upload Plugin</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"177\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-upload-plugin-button-1024x177.png\" alt=\"wordpress upload plugin button\" class=\"wp-image-210861\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-upload-plugin-button-1024x177.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-upload-plugin-button-300x52.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-upload-plugin-button-768x133.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-upload-plugin-button-1536x266.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-upload-plugin-button-600x104.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-upload-plugin-button-190x33.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-upload-plugin-button-519x90.png 519w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wordpress-upload-plugin-button.png 1962w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Then click <strong>Choose File</strong> and select the AIOSEO zip file from your computer.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"357\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/wordpress-choose-file-1024x357.png\" alt=\"wordpress choose plugin file\" class=\"wp-image-229871\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/wordpress-choose-file-1024x357.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/wordpress-choose-file-300x104.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/wordpress-choose-file-768x267.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/wordpress-choose-file-1536x535.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/wordpress-choose-file-2048x713.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/wordpress-choose-file-600x209.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/wordpress-choose-file-172x60.png 172w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/wordpress-choose-file-258x90.png 258w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, click <strong>Install Now</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-3-activate-the-plugin\">Step 3: Activate the Plugin</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A setup wizard will now walk you through a few steps.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s it! You’re ready to start improving your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Let&#039;s Go Through The All In One SEO Setup Wizard (Step-By-Step)\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xU4iZXdPIDY?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing\">Get AIOSEO Pro Now</a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-frequently-asked-questions-on-aioseo-free-trial\">Frequently Asked Questions on AIOSEO Free Trial</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-does-aioseo-have-a-free-version\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Does AIOSEO have a free version?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Yes, AIOSEO (All in One SEO) has a free version called AIOSEO Lite. This free plugin is available only on WordPress.org. There&#8217;s no need to enter credit card details. And there&#8217;s no time limit on the use of the free version.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Make sure that you only download a free version of All in One SEO from WordPress.org. Some sites sell <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/tag/all-in-one-seo-pro-pack-nulled/\">unauthorized copies of AIOSEO, laden with malware</a>. These knock-off versions are marketed under terms like AIOSEO nulled, AIOSEO cracked, and AIOSEO GPL.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-is-there-a-free-version-of-all-in-one-seo\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Is there a free version of All in One SEO?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Yes, there is a free version of All in One SEO called AIOSEO Lite. Download this free plugin, which has no time limit on usage, from<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/\"> </a><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">this WordPress.org page</a>. The WordPress.org site is the only authorized provider of AIOSEO Lite.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/aioseo-pro-nulled-security-warning/\" title=\"\">avoid malware</a>, do not download All in One SEO (AIOSEO) from any site other than WordPress.org or AIOSEO.com.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-is-aioseo-lite-free\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Is AIOSEO Lite free?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Yes, AIOSEO Lite is free. There&#8217;s no time limit for using AIOSEO Lite, and no credit card details are required. AIOSEO Lite is available for download on <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">this WordPress.org page</a>.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-is-it-worth-paying-for-aioseo\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Is it worth paying for AIOSEO?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>We recommend purchasing a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/#pricing-table\">paid version</a> of the plugin if you want to get the full benefits of All in One SEO (AIOSEO), such as local SEO and Link Assistant.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike many software products, AIOSEO charges an annual, not a monthly, fee. With thousands of 5-star reviews on WordPress.org, All in One SEO is a low-cost, high-value option.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-can-you-improve-seo-for-free\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Can you improve SEO for free?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Yes, you can improve SEO for free. For example, quality is the #1 ranking factor, and improving content quality can be done without purchasing courses or software. Additionally, you can quickly learn the basics of SEO from free online content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Many find that SEO plugins, like All in One SEO (AIOSEO), make SEO easy and efficient. Technical tasks become as easy as clicking buttons and filling out form fields. No coding knowledge is required. The plugin handles most technical SEO tasks automatically. This makes SEO plugins a good choice for beginners and time-strapped entrepreneurs.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-is-aioseo-free-on-wordpress\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Is AIOSEO free on WordPress?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Yes, AIOSEO has a free version, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-seo-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">AIOSEO Lite, available on WordPress.org</a>.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-comes-after-aioseo-lite\">What Comes After AIOSEO Lite?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know how to get a free version of All in One SEO (AIOSEO), what&#8217;s next?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Why not try one of our<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/diy-seo-projects-for-beginners/\"> DIY SEO projects for beginners</a>? And discover key differences between<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-vs-social-media/\"> SEO and social media</a>, so you save time.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find lots of valuable tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter</a>), <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-get-an-unlimited-free-trial-of-aioseo-lite/\">AIOSEO Lite: How to Get an Unlimited Free Trial of All in One SEO (100% Free Forever)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-get-an-unlimited-free-trial-of-aioseo-lite/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"How to Generate Robots.txt Files in WordPress [No Code] \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:154:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-generate-robots-txt-files-in-wordpress/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-generate-robots-txt-files-in-wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-generate-robots-txt-files-in-wordpress/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 25 Sep 2023 13:09:33 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"generate robots.txt\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"robots.txt files\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"what is robots.txt\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=228938\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:432:\"<p>Would you like to know how to generate robots.txt files in WordPress? A robots.txt file helps you control how search bots interact with your site. This makes it a very handy SEO tool for those who know how to use&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-generate-robots-txt-files-in-wordpress/\">How to Generate Robots.txt Files in WordPress [No Code] </a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18615:\"<p>Would you like to know how to generate robots.txt files in WordPress?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A robots.txt file helps you control how search bots interact with your site. This makes it a very handy SEO tool for those who know how to use it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you how to generate a robots.txt file in WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-a-robots-txt-file\">What is a Robots.txt File</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-generate-a-robots-txt-file-in-wordpress\">How to Generate a Robots.txt File In WordPress</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-1-install-aioseo\">Step 1: Install AIOSEO</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-2-access-the-robots-txt-editor\">Step 2: Access the Robots.txt Editor</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-3-add-robots-txt-directives\">Step 3: Add Robots.txt Directives</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-4-import-robots-txt-directives-from-another-site-optional\">Step 4: Import Robots.txt Directives from Another Site (Optional)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-5-test-your-robots-txt-file\">Step 5: Test Your Robots.txt File</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-generate-a-robots-txt-file-in-wordpress-your-faqs-answered\">How to Generate a Robots.txt File In WordPress: Your FAQs Answered</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-the-purpose-of-a-robots-txt-file\">What is the purpose of a robots.txt file?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-can-i-generate-robots-txt-in-wordpress\">How can I generate robots.txt in WordPress?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-can-i-manually-create-a-robots-txt-file-for-my-wordpress-site\">Can I manually create a robots.txt file for my WordPress site?</a></li></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-a-robots-txt-file\">What is a Robots.txt File</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-robots-txt-in-wordpress/\" title=\"What is Robots.txt in WordPress? [Beginner’s Guide]\">Robots.txt</a> is a text file that website owners can create to tell search engine bots how to interact with their sites, mainly which pages to crawl and which to ignore. In essence, that acts as your site’s gatekeeper and is stored in the root directory (also known as the main folder) of your website.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is what it looks like:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/what-is-robotstxt-example.png\" alt=\"Example of robots.txt\" class=\"wp-image-225741\" style=\"width:490px;height:199px\" width=\"490\" height=\"199\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/what-is-robotstxt-example.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/what-is-robotstxt-example-300x122.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/what-is-robotstxt-example-600x244.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can easily access your robots.txt file by visiting <em>https://yoursite.com/robots.txt.</em>&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some things you can use a robots.txt file for:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-crawling-and-indexing/\" title=\"What is Crawling and Indexing in SEO? [Beginners Guide]\">Control crawling</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Direct indexing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Prevent duplicate content issues</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Protect sensitive information</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Optimizes crawl budget&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Enhances site performance&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Despite being a simple text file, having an optimized robots.txt file can significantly impact your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-how-to-generate-a-robots-txt-file-in-wordpress\">How to Generate a Robots.txt File In WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to generate robots.txt files?</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: WordPress automatically generates a robots.txt file for your site. But usually, the default file may need to be optimized.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>The steps below will show you how to generate a custom robots.txt file. Don’t worry. No code or technical knowledge is needed.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-1-install-aioseo\">Step 1: Install AIOSEO</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The first step to generating custom robots.txt files is to install and activate <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO is a handy tool if you want to know how to generate robots.txt files in WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-96547\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a> is a powerful yet easy-to-use SEO plugin that boasts over 3 million active installs. Millions of smart bloggers use AIOSEO to help them boost their search engine rankings and drive qualified traffic to their blogs. The plugin has many powerful features and modules to help you properly configure your SEO settings. Examples include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Search Statistics:</strong> This powerful <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/search-statistics/\" title=\"Search Statistics\">Google Search Console integration</a> lets you track your keyword rankings and see important SEO metrics with 1-click, and more.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Next-gen Schema generator</strong>: This no-code schema generator enables users to generate and output any schema markup on your site.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Redirection Manager</strong>: Helps you manage redirects and eliminate 404 errors, making it easier for search engines to crawl and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/index-your-website-on-google/\" title=\"10 Quick &amp; Easy Ways to Index Your Website on Google\">index your site</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Link Assistant</strong>: Powerful <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/internal-link-assistant/\" title=\"Link Assistant\">internal linking tool</a> that automates building links between pages on your site. It also gives you an audit of outbound links.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>SEO Preview</strong>: This gives you an overview of your search and social snippets and general SEO so you can improve your optimization.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>IndexNow:</strong> For fast indexing on search engines that support the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/indexnow/\" title=\"IndexNow\">IndexNow protocol</a> (like Bing and Yandex).</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Sitemap generator</strong>: Automatically generate <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-a-sitemap-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Create a Sitemap in WordPress (The Easy Way)\">different types of sitemaps</a> to notify all search engines of any updates on your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\" title=\"Features\">And more</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check out our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And one of the most loved features is our advanced robots.txt editor. This powerful tool makes it easy to customize your robots.txt file to suit your needs. Plus, it also automatically adds your sitemap URLs to the robots.txt file!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-2-access-the-robots-txt-editor\">Step 2: Access the Robots.txt Editor</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you’ve activated AIOSEO, the next step is to access AIOSEO’s Robots.txt Editor. To do that, go to your AIOSEO menu and click <strong>Tools <strong>»</strong> Robots.txt Editor</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"502\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1.png\" alt=\"How to generate a robots.txt file in WordPress using AIOSEO.\" class=\"wp-image-222049\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1-300x215.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1-600x429.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1-84x60.png 84w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1-126x90.png 126w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, click on the <strong>Enable Custom Robots.txt</strong> toggle. Doing so enables you to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-edit-a-robots-txt-file-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Easily Edit a Robots.txt File in WordPress (Step by Step)\">edit your robots.txt file</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"438\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nerate-robotstxt-enable-editing.png\" alt=\"To generate robots.txt files, enable Custom Robots.txt.\" class=\"wp-image-228956\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nerate-robotstxt-enable-editing.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nerate-robotstxt-enable-editing-300x187.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nerate-robotstxt-enable-editing-600x374.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-3-add-robots-txt-directives\">Step 3: Add Robots.txt Directives</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you’ve enabled editing of your robots.txt files, the next step is to add your custom directives.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These are the instructions you want search bots to follow. Examples include <strong>Allow</strong>, <strong>Disallow</strong>, <strong>Clean-param</strong>, and <strong>Crawl delay</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives.png\" alt=\"Robots.txt directives\" class=\"wp-image-221028\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives-300x182.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives-600x364.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives-99x60.png 99w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives-148x90.png 148w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s what each directive means:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Allow</strong>: Allows user agents (bots) to crawl the URL.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Disallow</strong>: Disallows user agents (bots) to crawl the URL.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Clean-param</strong>: Tells search bots to ignore all URLs with the stipulated URL parameters.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Crawl-delay</strong>: Sets the intervals for search bots to crawl the URL.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>In this section, you can also determine which user agents should follow the directive. You’ll also have to stipulate the value (URL, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-delete-url-parameters-from-google-search-console/\" title=\"How to Delete URL Parameters from Google Search Console (The Easy Way)\">URL parameters</a>, or frequency) of the directive.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-4-import-robots-txt-directives-from-another-site-optional\">Step 4: Import Robots.txt Directives from Another Site (Optional)</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A simpler way to generate robots.txt files in WordPress is to use the <strong>Import</strong> function.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"321\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import.png\" alt=\"Import robots.txt\" class=\"wp-image-221031\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-300x137.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-600x274.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-131x60.png 131w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-197x90.png 197w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Clicking the Import button will open a window with 2 options for importing your chosen robots.txt file:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"492\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-1.png\" alt=\"You can import a robots.txt file from a URL or copying and pasting the file into your editor.\" class=\"wp-image-220397\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-1.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-1-300x210.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-1-600x421.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-1-86x60.png 86w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-1-128x90.png 128w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Import from URL</strong>: Simply paste the URL of the robots.txt file you want to import (<em>https://examplesite.com/robots.txt</em>) and click <strong>Import</strong>. The robots.txt file will be imported to your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Paste Robots.txt text</strong>: Open the URL with the robots.txt file you want to import and copy the text. Next, go back to your site, paste it into the provided field, and click <strong>Import</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This method is best if the site you’re importing the robots.txt file from has directives you would like to implement on your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-5-test-your-robots-txt-file\">Step 5: Test Your Robots.txt File</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you’re done generating your robots.txt file, you can test it for any errors. However, this is very rare if you use AIOSEO’s robots.txt editor, as it has built-in rule validation and error handling.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"710\" height=\"477\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/robots-error.png\" alt=\"Test for errors after generating robots.txt files.\" class=\"wp-image-220013\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/robots-error.png 710w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/robots-error-300x202.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/robots-error-600x403.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/robots-error-89x60.png 89w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/robots-error-134x90.png 134w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>However, if you want to double-check that there are no errors in your robots.txt file, you can use Google Search Console’s robots.txt testing tool. Simply enter your property, and the tool will automatically pull your robots.txt file and highlight any errors.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-how-to-generate-a-robots-txt-file-in-wordpress-your-faqs-answered\">How to Generate a Robots.txt File In WordPress: Your FAQs Answered</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-the-purpose-of-a-robots-txt-file\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What is the purpose of a robots.txt file?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>A robots.txt file provides instructions to search engine crawlers about which parts of your website they are allowed to access and index. It helps control how search engines interact with your site&#8217;s content.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-how-can-i-generate-robots-txt-in-wordpress\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">How can I generate robots.txt in WordPress?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>You can easily generate a robots.txt file in WordPress using a plugin like All In One SEO (AIOSEO). You don’t even need coding or technical knowledge.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-can-i-manually-create-a-robots-txt-file-for-my-wordpress-site\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Can I manually create a robots.txt file for my WordPress site?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Yes, you can manually create a robots.txt file using a text editor and place it in your site&#8217;s root directory. This takes longer than using a plugin like AIOSEO and requires advanced WordPress knowledge.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you know what robots.txt in WordPress is and why it’s important to optimize yours. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-crawling-and-indexing/\">guide on crawling and indexing</a> and its impact on SEO or our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/index-your-website-on-google/\">tips on improving your indexing on Google</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-generate-robots-txt-files-in-wordpress/\">How to Generate Robots.txt Files in WordPress [No Code] </a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-generate-robots-txt-files-in-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\"